raysync_title: RAYSYNC ENTERPRISE HIGH-SPEED LARGE FILE TRANSFER SOLUTION
raysync_text_0: Raysync is a high-speed large file transfer solution that focuses on providing enterprises with a secure and controllable transfer solution.
raysync_text_1: Based on cloud computing, the internet, and big data architecture applications, Raysync’s independently developed ultra-high-speed transmission protocol can easily meet the demand for rapid transmission of TB-level large files and massive small files, achieving a speed increase of 100 times.
raysync_text_2: As a leading brand in enterprise-level large file transfer, Raysync has provided efficient and secure file distribution, file sharing, data organization, and synchronization services to enterprises across various fields, including IT and the internet, finance, film, biotechnology, and manufacturing.
cat3d_text: 3DCAT is an AI + XR real-time rendering solution based on the concept of cloud computing. 3DCAT can run your XR applications in the cloud, and stream their rendered frames and audio to browsers and XR devices, which can give an more immersive interactive experience to all end-users anytime, anywhere.
